{"tid":2324900,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真討論] 係咪越來越多香港人有情緒病？","createTime":"2020-12-14T09:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T17:51:08.000Z","uid":73959,"like":12,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff35ec5fa2e69dc7b699ede62b5e13816a83575","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:23:33.000Z","msg":"自從舊年返送中<br />\n好多唔公平、慘不忍睹、令人憤怒嘅事發生咗<br />\n社會上有兩種不同嘅聲音 互相指責對方<br />\n就算同一陣線 都互相鬥黃<br />\n<br />\n到今年有武漢肺炎 有人恐懼病毒<br />\n有人因此失業<br />\n仲有份工嘅都唔代表係好 WFH變咗廿四小時on call<br />\n做得唔開心又唔敢轉工 <br />\n加上唔係個個屋企都有自己私人空間<br />\n日復日屈喺一個豆腐潤屋企<br />\n<br />\n雖然外國都有受疫情影響<br />\n但至少佢哋活動範圍比較大 加上冇政治迫壓<br />\n真心想知以上情況下 會唔會越來越多香港人有情緒病？<br />\n只係大家係冇為意 未浮現出嚟<br />\n定係只係個別性格問題？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我冇事日日過得好開心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都有唔開心 懷疑自己情緒都有啲問題"},{"pid":"a2140ef7512777386fa6bce8f47f47d2b79ab84d","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"過得好開心嘅不如都分享吓你點樣保持正面心態？<br />\n<br />\n如果係有錢人 唔使返工唔憂柴米同住大屋嗰啲可以唔使講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc3ea53f14f58217409ca5452de4131fe32741c","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"過得唔開心嘅 不如分享吓你嘅煩惱係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a997ce89a21faea0d26116dd35b62c497bb35f0","tid":2324900,"uid":115082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2140ef7512777386fa6bce8f47f47d2b79ab84d","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"過得好開心嘅不如都分享吓你點樣保持正面心態？<br />\n<br />\n如果係有錢人 唔使返工唔憂柴米同住大屋嗰啲可以唔使講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"連登無人住細屋架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2d8572c3190a95f53d090210251b5b69714d74","tid":2324900,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc3ea53f14f58217409ca5452de4131fe32741c","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"過得唔開心嘅 不如分享吓你嘅煩惱係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想轉工 我想加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想搬去第二度住"},{"pid":"ad00cb13ad8d3980ac7b72e79def851e90a538d0","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a2d8572c3190a95f53d090210251b5b69714d74","tid":2324900,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fc3ea53f14f58217409ca5452de4131fe32741c","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"過得唔開心嘅 不如分享吓你嘅煩惱係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想轉工 我想加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想搬去第二度住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:28:18.000Z","msg":"同我煩惱一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都係為錢 為住屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6739b8d71943c475a2494a6aaa9a8291d3736c3e","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:30:26.000Z","msg":"或者有做呢類型學術研究嘅都可以分享吓喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得城市人開唔開心 或者情緒病問題<br />\n都同當地政治、生活同文化環境有直接影響"},{"pid":"f0a19f0c76201895831ca786cb9fd5fd212a0b8d","tid":2324900,"uid":265270,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:30:46.000Z","msg":"認真，去唔到旅行勁抑鬱，留喺香港抖唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c430f8b47abe1c0882b4870556dcc73ecc7117","tid":2324900,"uid":8681,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:30:50.000Z","msg":"香港所有野都係垃圾，淨係想走。"},{"pid":"476cba9bb9f02ae3e161b4dd378e0831811cf222","tid":2324900,"uid":238415,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得情緒病既界限比以前高左<br />\n換轉係早多四五十年前<br />\n以依家好多香港人既情緒狀況可能已經被診斷為情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 我好耐之前已經覺得自己有情緒病...似係靠理性壓左落黎"},{"pid":"b333ead8168b853efa66f82f89f79c0953378129","tid":2324900,"uid":265270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"44c430f8b47abe1c0882b4870556dcc73ecc7117","tid":2324900,"uid":8681,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:30:50.000Z","msg":"香港所有野都係垃圾，淨係想走。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"不能認同更多，好辛苦留係度"},{"pid":"1c37b8837cb76b89506ab9cd4bd2bbf807479faa","tid":2324900,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44c430f8b47abe1c0882b4870556dcc73ecc7117","tid":2324900,"uid":8681,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:30:50.000Z","msg":"香港所有野都係垃圾，淨係想走。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:33:01.000Z","msg":"多謝手足爭取bno平權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46fb2af9cbd4a9e268840edecb8867d560f4a0e","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0a19f0c76201895831ca786cb9fd5fd212a0b8d","tid":2324900,"uid":265270,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:30:46.000Z","msg":"認真，去唔到旅行勁抑鬱，留喺香港抖唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:34:22.000Z","msg":"加入選項 ☑️冇得去旅行而感到抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n當有得去返旅行就無事㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afaf626c07020ec6595e1dc1460949e0aab62c3","tid":2324900,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"好多人放工OR失業...連係間屋打飛機空間都冇"},{"pid":"b5c35228ce1ea107e2e84a5026a2cad4f7e64314","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44c430f8b47abe1c0882b4870556dcc73ecc7117","tid":2324900,"uid":8681,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:30:50.000Z","msg":"香港所有野都係垃圾，淨係想走。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:36:53.000Z","msg":"明白嘅 咁你係已經有打算移民定係因為某啲原因走唔到？"},{"pid":"dd038959ac6a45e02ec78421e5dadbf6b0889454","tid":2324900,"uid":84432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"屋企冇私人空間 <br />\n唔知自己想點（工作發展之類）<br />\n社會環境<br />\n<br />\n我想開心少少咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58906aa2a718601c9e2dc6df631496511afb13cc","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"476cba9bb9f02ae3e161b4dd378e0831811cf222","tid":2324900,"uid":238415,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:31:52.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得情緒病既界限比以前高左<br />\n換轉係早多四五十年前<br />\n以依家好多香港人既情緒狀況可能已經被診斷為情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 我好耐之前已經覺得自己有情緒病...似係靠理性壓左落黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:41:47.000Z","msg":"做個問卷測下你有冇情緒病：<br />\n<br />\n假如你兩個星期內差不多大部分時間出現下列五項或以上的症狀 (必須包括1或2) ，嚴重影響日常生活、學業或社交活動，你可能患上抑鬱症，請你立即尋求專業協助<br />\n<br />\n1. 情緒低落、煩躁、經常發脾氣<br />\n2. 納悶、失去對事物、活動的興趣，如運動、打遊戲機或以往喜愛的活動<br />\n3. 食慾不振、暴食或體重驟降/驟升<br />\n4. 很難入睡、拒絕起床返學、早醒或渴睡<br />\n5. 行動遲滯或說話/行為比平時激動<br />\n6. 感到疲累、精力不充或無精打采<br />\n7. 專注力下降、失去學習動機<br />\n8. 容易過分內疚、自責或覺得無人喜歡自己<br />\n9. 反覆有死亡、自殺念頭，寫遺書或把自己最愛的物件送給別人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hmdc.cuhk.edu.hk/depression-test/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hmdc.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fdepression-test%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725L32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=6e6af0c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hmdc.cuhk.edu.hk/depression-test/</a>"},{"pid":"d6cada0a381cd4a2af3e1ea936ac707c087dbf74","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd038959ac6a45e02ec78421e5dadbf6b0889454","tid":2324900,"uid":84432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"屋企冇私人空間 <br />\n唔知自己想點（工作發展之類）<br />\n社會環境<br />\n<br />\n我想開心少少咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"加入選項 <br />\n☑️住屋問題 (私人空間)<br />\n☑️工作發展 (晉升、轉工)<br />\n☑️社會環境 (政治、福利)<br />\n☑️冇得去旅行"},{"pid":"2113bbf351b7b034240654ecaa5e437806eb1a11","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:45:37.000Z","msg":"過得開心嗰啲分享吓吖<br />\n將你哋嘅正能量share出去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65ef4be92d9494d5c2000e058f9dc560e2cb4cc","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2afaf626c07020ec6595e1dc1460949e0aab62c3","tid":2324900,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"好多人放工OR失業...連係間屋打飛機空間都冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"即係都係住屋問題同埋工作問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ec246e5e4a21ddbced6716de60965f6f3d0557","tid":2324900,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"抵死戴口罩呀拿"},{"pid":"030c9342efbd25da5afe885a227ba2b3ef8db176","tid":2324900,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62ec246e5e4a21ddbced6716de60965f6f3d0557","tid":2324900,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"抵死戴口罩呀拿"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:49:33.000Z","msg":"關乜嘢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass